headline: Ocean Park Asset Management Named Finalist for 2025 MMI/Barron’s Industry Awards
summary: LOS ANGELES, September 23, 2025--Ocean Park Asset Management has been named a finalist for the 2025 MMI/Barron’s Industry Awards in the Marketing Campaign of the Year category.
